text: Suryakumar Ashok Yadav is a professional cricketer from India. Yadav plays for the Indian national cricket team and for the Mumbai cricket team in Indian domestic cricket. In the Indian premier league, he plays for Mumbai Indians and serves as the vice-captain for the team. He was born on September 14, 1990. == References == == Other websites == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Mumbai
